                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5815" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0430</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9470 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">乾坤未定，你我皆是黑马—九机游戏化绩效管理的衍变之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">We are all the Winners in the Horse Racing:9JI.COM’s  Journey towards to the Reform of Performance Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄波，王延玲，谢立新，江新会，黄丽丽，赵佳豪，王文棚，刘洋君，魏鑫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南九机电子产品有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">九机；游戏化；绩效管理；赛马；2022百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9JI.COM; gamification; Performance Management; “Horse Racing” </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">九机是云南唯一一家中国互联网百强企业，作为一家主要团队成员由90和95后组成的创业公司，在绩效管理上不能一味按照老旧的管理模式进行。经过探索及沉淀，九机针对分公司等独立经营单元，摸索出一条具备“游戏化思维”的绩效管理模式即“赛马”，“赛马”游戏化绩效管理体系利用九机的OA系统可多维度、实时呈现考核指标及完成情况，再加之匹配了相应的赛马金进行了及时奖励，充分调动了员工的工作积极性，使得九机在市场上的占有率、竞争力不断提升。本案例描述了九机针对分公司的游戏化绩效管理模式的“赛马”从无到有的发展历程，从一代“赛马”规划、试点打样、发现问题、提出解决方案、到不断提炼优化发展到二代“赛马”，之后推广到全面游戏化绩效管理体系的方案落地与实施。本案例以真实事件为背景，期望读者能基于绩效管理方面的相关知识，对案例提出的决策性问题进行分析并思考相应对策。同时为我国企业进一步结合外部环境和自身特点，并创新和引进先进的绩效管理模式提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">9JI.COM is the one of Chinese top 100 internet companies in Yunnan. As a start-up company composed of members in post-90s and post-95s, it is not suitable for it to blindly follow the traditional performance management mode. After exploration and accumulation, 9JI.COM has explored a performance management mode with &quot;gamification&quot; for its independent business units such as branches, namely &quot;Horse Racing&quot;. With successful designing of assessment indicators in multi-dimensional and real-time, and clear information presentation of completion of task indicators, the system continuously help to improve 9JI.COM’s market share and competitiveness. This case describes the development process of 9JI.COM’s “Horse Racing” performance management system it terms of its first scratching, continuous refining and optimization, and its gradual improvement. On the basis of real events, the readers are expected to analyze the decision-making problems and think about the corresponding countermeasures according to their own relevant knowledge of performance management. At the same time, it provides reference for Chinese enterprises so as to innovate and introduce their advanced performance management mode based on their own characteristics.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《绩效管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绩效管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-12</td>
                            </tr>
